title: Hey, Kylie Jenner, here's a bunch of things you can trademark besides your name
text:
'Kylie' may not be available but you still have options!
Kylie Jenner , cosmetic connoisseur and dog mom, recently lost a trademark battle for her first name against Kylie Minogue , the Australian singer. The Kylies had been fighting over the trademark 'Kylie' in the U.S. but, in the end, Minogue won and blocked Jenner from owning the name.
SEE ALSO: There can only be one Kylie‚Ñ¢ and it's not that Jenner one
But, the situation does have a bit of a silver lining; Jenner has a new hobby. She can now shop around and find other things to trademark and get some badly-needed lessons on the legal system in the process.
